---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Discordium.org Investigation">
  <main class="bg-neutral-950 text-white min-h-screen px-6 py-12">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-16 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
        Discordium.org: An Ongoing Pattern of Misconduct
      </h1>
      <p class="text-neutral-300 text-lg">
        Discordium presents itself as a professional Discord advertising service.
        Evidence and testimonies from multiple sources suggest a consistent pattern
        of harassment, data misuse, and policy violations.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- SUMMARY -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 border-b border-neutral-800 pb-2">
        Overview
      </h2>

      <p class="text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
        Discordium.org, operated by Nassvoll (Aljoscha Klemcke), advertises itself as a legitimate platform
        for Discord server promotion. However, collected evidence indicates repeated involvement in:
      </p>

      <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-neutral-300">
        <li>• Harassment and retaliation against critics</li>
        <li>• Non-consensual sharing of personal information (doxxing)</li>
        <li>• Public admissions of predatory or illegal behavior by staff</li>
        <li>• Violations of Discord Terms of Service</li>
        <li>• GDPR compliance failures</li>
        <li>• Copyright infringement and false ownership claims</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- INCIDENT: WEBHOOK RAID -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 border-b border-neutral-800 pb-2">
        Recent Incident: Webhook Abuse & Server Raid
      </h2>

      <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-6">
        A Discordium administrator triggered mass webhook spam, repeatedly pinging entire servers
        while broadcasting accusations involving internal staff. Only administrators had access
        to these webhook systems.
      </p>

      <!-- 🔴 IMAGE PLACEHOLDER -->
      <img src="/images/webhook-raid.png" alt="Webhook spam incident" class="rounded-lg mb-4 border border-neutral-800" />
      <!-- Upload image to: /public/images/webhook-raid.png -->

      <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">
        Screenshot: Public logs showing repeated webhook messages and admin-level access behavior
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- PREDATOR COVER-UP -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 border-b border-neutral-800 pb-2">
        Internal Admissions & Staff Protection
      </h2>

      <p class="text-neutral-300">
        Evidence shows internal acknowledgment of serious misconduct within staff ranks,
        including allegations involving predatory behavior. Despite this, individuals remained active
        or were quietly removed without explanation.
      </p>

      <!-- 🔴 IMAGE -->
      <img src="/images/predator-admission.png" class="rounded-lg mt-6 border border-neutral-800" />
      <!-- /public/images/predator-admission.png -->

      <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm mt-2">
        Internal messages indicating awareness and lack of enforcement
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- DOXXING -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 border-b border-neutral-800 pb-2">
        Doxxing & Personal Data Exposure
      </h2>

      <p class="text-neutral-300">
        Multiple staff members, including leadership, have been documented sharing personal
        information without consent. This includes Discord IDs and other identifying data,
        in direct violation of platform policies.
      </p>

      <!-- 🔴 IMAGE -->
      <img src="/images/doxxing-proof.png" class="rounded-lg mt-6 border border-neutral-800" />
      <!-- /public/images/doxxing-proof.png -->
    </section>

    <!-- RETALIATION -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 border-b border-neutral-800 pb-2">
        Retaliation Against Reports
      </h2>

      <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-300">
        <li>• Users reporting misconduct are banned</li>
        <li>• Evidence is deleted or dismissed</li>
        <li>• Legal threats are used to silence criticism</li>
        <li>• Reviews are repeatedly flagged for removal</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- 🔴 IMAGE -->
      <img src="/images/threats.png" class="rounded-lg mt-6 border border-neutral-800" />
      <!-- /public/images/threats.png -->
    </section>

    <!-- GDPR -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 border-b border-neutral-800 pb-2">
        GDPR Compliance Issues
      </h2>

      <p class="text-neutral-300">
        Discordium claims GDPR compliance, yet their Data Protection Officer appears to be the same
        individual as the owner. This conflicts with GDPR Article 38, which requires independence
        in data protection oversight.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- COPYRIGHT -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 border-b border-neutral-800 pb-2">
        False Ownership & Copyright Concerns
      </h2>

      <p class="text-neutral-300">
        Staff members have claimed ownership of major Discord bots such as MEE6, Carl, and Pokétwo.
        Original developers have confirmed these claims are false.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- EXTERNAL VALIDATION -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 border-b border-neutral-800 pb-2">
        External Actions & Verification
      </h2>

      <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-300">
        <li>• Trustpilot verified multiple reports as genuine</li>
        <li>• Discord servers have blacklisted Discordium</li>
        <li>• Listing platforms have removed their presence</li>
        <li>• Legal and regulatory bodies have acknowledged complaints</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- FULL REPORT -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
      <a href="YOUR_GOOGLE_DOC_LINK"
         class="inline-block bg-white text-black px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-neutral-200 transition">
        View Full 67-Page Report
      </a>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>
